 看另一則問題 










            中文翻譯英文一句話(有關理論運用在實務上)
        


我期許能將所學的理論有效的運用在未來的實務上 

請勿用翻譯軟體





 
追蹤 


 
 5 個解答 
5


檢舉不當使用









您確定要刪除此解答嗎？
是
否












 









抱歉，似乎發生一些問題。



Trending Now





 

解答


評分


最新
最舊














最佳解答: 
             I look forward to put the theory I learned into practice effectively in the future affairs. 
或者 
I expect to put the theory I learned into practice effectively in the future affairs. 
或者 
I expect to effectively apply the theory I learned to the future affiars. 
或者麻煩一點用關代子句 
I expect that I can effectively apply the theory I learned to the future affairs. 

put something into practice 實行某樣事物 
apply something to 運用；實行某樣事物 
look foward to 期盼 
expect to 希望 




